The Holy Grail of Hair has arrived on @mynykaa! ✨

From effortless curls and beachy waves to red carpet-ready looks, GHD gives me the freedom to create a variety of styles. I’m super excited to be a part of the GHD Army and can’t wait to celebrate the launch at @nykaaland with a masterclass that I will be hosting on 26th October.

So grab your festival passes and come discover the GHD range this weekend.

#NykaaxGHD #OnlyOnNykaa #NewLaunch #GHDArmy

From beachy waves to glam curls – GHD Chronos does it all! 💫 3 ways to curl, endless styles to slay 😍 

Shop the exclusive GHD range now on Nykaa! 💕

#Nykaa #NykaaxGHD #OnlyOnNykaa #GHDArmy

We’re thrilled to welcome Yianni Tsapatori, an internationally acclaimed hairstylist and celebrity favourite, as our Creative Director (Hair). With 25 years of experience and an illustrious portfolio, he’s set to bring his unparalleled expertise to Godrej Professional.

You now have the chance to work with him at Spotlight by Godrej Professional.

This is your chance to shine alongside the industry’s finest hairstylists like @yiannitsapatori @shailesh_moolya and @najeeb.rehmaan 

Participate in Spotlight by Godrej Professional and let the world witness your talent!

Click the link in the bio to register. 

#GodrejProfessional #Spotlight #ParticipateNow #RegistrationsOpen #ContestAlert #SpotlightByGodrejProfessional

Inspired by the ethereal Pyramids of Giza, celebrated hairstylists, Yianni Tsapatori, Shailesh Moolya, and Najeeb Ur Rehman have crafted a Surreal colour. Moffee Marvel, an exquisite blend of rich mocha and coffee hues offers the most charming makeover. A look so timeless and sophisticated, that it takes everyone’s breath away.

Recommend it today and let your clients embrace elegance.

Recreate the look and stand a chance to be selected for Spotlight, a competition for hairdressers to showcase exceptional hairdressing artistry!

Click the link in the bio to register. 

#GodrejProfessional #SurrealCollection #SurrealLaunch #HairStyle #HairColourLaunch #MoonlitMist

Witness Yianni Tsapatori, Shailesh Moolya, and Najeeb Ur Rehman bring Surreal by Godrej Professional to life. It is a collection of four enchanting looks that are inspired by nature.

You can recreate one of the looks and stand a chance to work with these maestros at Spotlight by Godrej Professional, a competition for hairdressers.

Here’s how you can participate:
- Choose a look from the Surreal Collection
- Tell us what inspired you to choose it
- Submit your entry

30 shortlisted participants will be invited to Mumbai.

3 winners will receive exciting prizes and the opportunity to work with a celebrity.

1st prize - ₹5 Lakhs
2nd prize - ₹2.5 Lakhs
3rd prize - ₹1.5 Lakhs

The Spotlight is awaiting you!

Click the link in the bio to register.

#GodrejProfessional #SurrealCollection #Spotlight #ParticipateNow #RegistrationsOpen #ContestAlert #SpotlightByGodrejProfessional

Drawing inspiration from the ravishing beauty of the Antelope Canyon, Tangerine Dream is a Surreal colour crafted by the maestros Yianni Tsapatori, Shailesh Moolya and Najeeb Ur Rehman.

With hues of shimmering gold and earthy copper, this look mesmerises everyone.

Introduce Tangerine Dream to your clients today!

Recreate the look and stand a chance to be selected for Spotlight, a competition for hairdressers to showcase exceptional hairdressing artistry!
